data.description: CAST5 block cipher in pure Perl
data.PS: The following links are only valid for module list maintainers:
data.rationale:
This module implements the CAST5 encryption algorithm in Perl. It
    has a similar interface to the other Crypt::* modules, and
    interoperates with Crypt::CBC.

    CAST5 is a freely available block cipher which is used in (for
    example) OpenPGP.

    Crypt::OpenSSL::BIO contains support for CAST5, however it requires
    the OpenSSL library. This perl implementation has no dependencies.
